e-simple-lemmatized\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Cspan data-text=\"Claudius\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Claudius\">Claudius\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"Maximus\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"Maximus\">Maximus\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"vixit\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"vivo\">vixit\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"annis\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"annus\">annis\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"XVII\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"XVII\">XVII\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Maria Randazzo\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"la\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\" Claudius ❦\n                    Maximus\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"nomen\" data-text=\"Claudius\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"Claudius\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Claudius\">CLAUD\u003C/span>\u003C/span>❦\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"cognomen\" data-text=\"Maximus\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"Maximus\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"Maximus\">MAXIMUS\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/span>❦\u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"vixit\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"vivo\">VIX\u003C/span>❦\u003Cspan data-text=\"annis\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"annus\">AN\u003C/span>.\u003Cspan data-text=\"XVII\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"XVII\">XVII\u003C/span>❦\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Victoria Fendel\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic-simple-lemmatized\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"Claudius\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Claudius\">CLAUDIUS\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"Maximus\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"Maximus\">MAXIMUS\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"vixit\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"vivo\">VIXIT\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"annis\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"annus\">ANNIS\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"XVII\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"XVII\">XVII\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic000056_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"Photo J. Prag, courtesy  Museo Archeologico Regionale Antonino Salinas\" src=\"ISic000056_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic000056.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"Photo J. Prag, courtesy  Museo Archeologico Regionale Antonino Salinas\" src=\"ISic000056-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>  \u003Cspan>Text from autopsy\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>Italian translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">Maria Randazzo\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>Claudio Massimo, visse per anni diciassette.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537\">Jonathan Prag\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>Claudius Maximus lived for 17 years.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>La lettura del testo è sostanzialmente identica alle edizioni precedenti (Mommsen- C.I.L. X - Bivona 1970). Il commento si discosta dall'edizione di Mommsen (l'unica a riportare i segni d'interpunzione) per l'interpretazione dei segni divisori, nelle linee 2 e 3, come piccole foglie d'edera stilizzate: questa lettura si deve al particolare del tratto allungato verso destra, più simile al gambo d'edera della prima linea (per quanto la grandezza differisce molto) che ad un semplice segno a sezione triangolare; inoltre, tra l'abbreviazione \"an\" di \"annis\" e il numerale \"XVII\", si scorge un segno obliquo molto simile al carattere prima descritto e quindi considerato come un segno divisorio a foglia d'edera incerto.\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>L'epigrafe funeraria è molto semplice, con formulario estremamente sintetico: viene riportato il nome del defunto (composto esclusivamente di nomen e cognomen) e la durata della vita. Sulla base di questa particolarità, Bivona data l'iscrizione ad un periodo antecedente a Marco Aurelio in quanto fu quest'ultimo a regolarizzare le norme sui tria nomina. La studiosa ricorda infatti che il praenomen, prima di quest'epoca, veniva assunto al compimento del diciassettesimo anno di vita con l'assunzione della toga virile; cerimonia che evidentemente in questo caso non era ancora avvenuta. Secondo il Mommsen, il reperto fu segnalato in un mercato antiquario a Termini Imerese nel 1867 da Benndorf. In un'età imprecisata, ma verosimilmente non in antico, furono ricavati due piccoli fori sullo spessore inferiore, probabilmente per l'esposizione della lastra.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Mommsen 1883 \u003Ca href=\"http://arachne.uni-koeln.de/item/buchseite/650798\" target=\"_blank\">7391\u003C/a>  \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Bivona 1970 56 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002142\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002142\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Bivona 1994 72 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002137\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002137\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"handnote\"> \u003Cp>The letters are v-cut in a tall and narrow module, with triangular serifs. The letters are regularly spaced, with the size / spacing decreasing towards the right and from line 1 to line 3. A has a cross bar descending to the left; M has four full length strokes, all off vertical. Interpuncts in the form of ivy-leaf (somewhat various in form) at the end of each line; plainer interpuncts between words in line 3.\u003C/p> Line 1  55  Line 2  52  Line 3  30    25    15  \u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. \u003C/div>",[253,256,259,262,265,267,270,273,276],{"id":254,"html":255},"editions","\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Maria Randazzo\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"la\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\" Claudius ❦\n                    Maximus\">  \u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"nomen\" data-text=\"Claudius\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"Claudius\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Claudius\">Claud(ius)\u003C/span>\u003C/span> ❦ \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"cognomen\" data-text=\"Maximus\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"Maximus\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"Maximus\">Maximus\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/span> ❦ \u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"vixit\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"vivo\">vix(it)\u003C/span> ❦ \u003Cspan data-text=\"annis\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"annus\">an(nis)\u003C/span> ❦ \u003Cspan data-text=\"XVII\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"XVII\">XVII\u003C/span> ❦ \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Victoria Fendel\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive-simple-lemmatized\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Cspan data-text=\"Claudius\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Claudius\">Claudius\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"Maximus\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"Maximus\">Maximus\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"vixit\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"vivo\">vixit\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"annis\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"annus\">annis\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"XVII\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"XVII\">XVII\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Maria Randazzo\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"la\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\" Claudius ❦\n                    Maximus\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"nomen\" data-text=\"Claudius\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"Claudius\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Claudius\">CLAUD\u003C/span>\u003C/span>❦\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"cognomen\" data-text=\"Maximus\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"Maximus\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"Maximus\">MAXIMUS\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/span>❦\u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"vixit\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"vivo\">VIX\u003C/span>❦\u003Cspan data-text=\"annis\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"annus\">AN\u003C/span>.\u003Cspan data-text=\"XVII\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"XVII\">XVII\u003C/span>❦\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Victoria Fendel\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic-simple-lemmatized\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"Claudius\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Claudius\">CLAUDIUS\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"Maximus\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"Maximus\">MAXIMUS\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"vixit\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"vivo\">VIXIT\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"annis\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"annus\">ANNIS\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"XVII\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"XVII\">XVII\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>",{"id":257,"html":258},"facsimile-images","\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic000056_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"Photo J. Prag, courtesy  Museo Archeologico Regionale Antonino Salinas\" src=\"ISic000056_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic000056.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"Photo J. Prag, courtesy  Museo Archeologico Regionale Antonino Salinas\" src=\"ISic000056-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>",{"id":260,"html":261},"apparatus","\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>  \u003Cspan>Text from autopsy\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>",{"id":263,"html":264},"translation","\u003Ch2>Italian translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">Maria Randazzo\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>Claudio Massimo, visse per anni diciassette.\u003C/p>  ",{"id":263,"html":266},"\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537\">Jonathan Prag\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>Claudius Maximus lived for 17 years.\u003C/p>  ",{"id":268,"html":269},"commentary","\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>La lettura del testo è sostanzialmente identica alle edizioni precedenti (Mommsen- C.I.L. X - Bivona 1970). Il commento si discosta dall'edizione di Mommsen (l'unica a riportare i segni d'interpunzione) per l'interpretazione dei segni divisori, nelle linee 2 e 3, come piccole foglie d'edera stilizzate: questa lettura si deve al particolare del tratto allungato verso destra, più simile al gambo d'edera della prima linea (per quanto la grandezza differisce molto) che ad un semplice segno a sezione triangolare; inoltre, tra l'abbreviazione \"an\" di \"annis\" e il numerale \"XVII\", si scorge un segno obliquo molto simile al carattere prima descritto e quindi considerato come un segno divisorio a foglia d'edera incerto.\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>L'epigrafe funeraria è molto semplice, con formulario estremamente sintetico: viene riportato il nome del defunto (composto esclusivamente di nomen e cognomen) e la durata della vita. Sulla base di questa particolarità, Bivona data l'iscrizione ad un periodo antecedente a Marco Aurelio in quanto fu quest'ultimo a regolarizzare le norme sui tria nomina. La studiosa ricorda infatti che il praenomen, prima di quest'epoca, veniva assunto al compimento del diciassettesimo anno di vita con l'assunzione della toga virile; cerimonia che evidentemente in questo caso non era ancora avvenuta. Secondo il Mommsen, il reperto fu segnalato in un mercato antiquario a Termini Imerese nel 1867 da Benndorf. In un'età imprecisata, ma verosimilmente non in antico, furono ricavati due piccoli fori sullo spessore inferiore, probabilmente per l'esposizione della lastra.\u003C/p>  ",{"id":271,"html":272},"bibliography","\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Mommsen 1883 \u003Ca href=\"http://arachne.uni-koeln.de/item/buchseite/650798\" target=\"_blank\">7391\u003C/a>  \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Bivona 1970 56 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002142\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002142\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Bivona 1994 72 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002137\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002137\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  ",{"id":274,"html":275},"handnote"," \u003Cp>The letters are v-cut in a tall and narrow module, with triangular serifs. The letters are regularly spaced, with the size / spacing decreasing towards the right and from line 1 to line 3. A has a cross bar descending to the left; M has four full length strokes, all off vertical. Interpuncts in the form of ivy-leaf (somewhat various in form) at the end of each line; plainer interpuncts between words in line 3.\u003C/p> Line 1  55  Line 2  52  Line 3  30    25    15  ",{"id":277,"html":278},"license"," Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. ",[280,282,285,287,290,291,294,295],{"html":281},"Text encoding: Maria Randazzo",{"id":283,"lang":136,"html":284},"edition-interpretive","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\" Claudius ❦\n                    Maximus\">  \u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"nomen\" data-text=\"Claudius\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"Claudius\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Claudius\">Claud(ius)\u003C/span>\u003C/span> ❦ \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"cognomen\" data-text=\"Maximus\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"Maximus\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"Maximus\">Maximus\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/span> ❦ \u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"vixit\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"vivo\">vix(it)\u003C/span> ❦ \u003Cspan data-text=\"annis\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"annus\">an(nis)\u003C/span> ❦ \u003Cspan data-text=\"XVII\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"XVII\">XVII\u003C/span> ❦ \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>",{"html":286},"Text encoding: Victoria Fendel",{"id":288,"html":289},"edition-interpretive-simple-lemmatized","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Cspan data-text=\"Claudius\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Claudius\">Claudius\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"Maximus\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"Maximus\">Maximus\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"vixit\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"vivo\">vixit\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"annis\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"annus\">annis\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"XVII\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"XVII\">XVII\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>",{"html":281},{"id":292,"lang":136,"html":293},"edition-diplomatic","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\" Claudius ❦\n                    Maximus\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"nomen\" data-text=\"Claudius\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"Claudius\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Claudius\">CLAUD\u003C/span>\u003C/span>❦\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"cognomen\" data-text=\"Maximus\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"Maximus\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"Maximus\">MAXIMUS\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/span>❦\u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"vixit\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"vivo\">VIX\u003C/span>❦\u003Cspan data-text=\"annis\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"annus\">AN\u003C/span>.\u003Cspan data-text=\"XVII\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"XVII\">XVII\u003C/span>❦\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>",{"html":286},{"id":296,"html":297},"edition-diplomatic-simple-lemmatized","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"Claudius\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Claudius\">CLAUDIUS\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"Maximus\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"Maximus\">MAXIMUS\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"vixit\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"vivo\">VIXIT\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"annis\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"annus\">ANNIS\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"XVII\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"XVII\">XVII\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>",[299,301],{"image":111,"thumb":300,"title":114},"ISic000056_tiled-thumb.tif",{"image":302,"thumb":303,"title":114},"ISic000056.jpg","ISic000056-thumb.jpg",[305],{"html":57},"\u003C?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n\u003C?xml-model href=\"https://epidoc.stoa.org/schema/latest/tei-epidoc.rng\" type=\"application/xml\" schematypens=\"http://relaxng.org/ns/structure/1.0\"?>\n\u003C?xml-model href=\"../schematron/ircyr-checking.sch\" schematypens=\"http://purl.oclc.org/dsdl/schematron\"?>\n\u003CTEI xmlns=\"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0\" xmlns:xi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude\" xml:lang=\"en\">\n    \u003CteiHeader>\n        \u003CfileDesc>\n            \u003CtitleStmt>\n                \u003Ctitle>Funerary inscription for Claudius Maximus\u003C/title>\n                \u003Ceditor ref=\"#JP\">Jonathan Prag\u003C/editor>\n                \u003Cprincipal ref=\"#JP\">Jonathan Prag\u003C/principal>\n                \u003Cfunder>John Fell OUP Research Fund\u003C/funder>\n                \u003Cfunder>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://cordis.europa.eu/project/id/885040\">ERC Advanced Grant no.885040\u003C/ref>\n                \u003C/funder>\n                \u003CrespStmt>\n                    \u003Cname xml:id=\"JP\" ref=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537\">Jonathan Prag\u003C/name>\n                    \u003Cresp>original data collection and editing\u003C/resp>\n                \u003C/respStmt>\n                \u003CrespStmt>\n                    \u003Cname xml:id=\"JCu\" ref=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0002-6686-3728\">James Cummings\u003C/name>\n                    \u003Cresp>conversion to EpiDoc\u003C/resp>\n                \u003C/respStmt>\n                \u003CrespStmt>\n                    \u003Cname xml:id=\"TA\" ref=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-8417-7089\">Tuuli Ahlholm\u003C/name>\n                    \u003Cresp>EpiDoc editing\u003C/resp>\n                \u003C/respStmt>\n                \u003CrespStmt>\n                    \u003Cname xml:id=\"SS\" ref=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0003-3914-9569\">Simona Stoyanova\u003C/name>\n                    \u003Cresp>standardisation of template and tidying up encoding\u003C/resp>\n                \u003C/respStmt>\n                \u003CrespStmt>\n                    \u003Cname xml:id=\"VM\" ref=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0002-7122-2511\">Valentina Mignosa\u003C/name>\n                    \u003Cresp>encoding text division\u003C/resp>\n                \u003C/respStmt>\n                \u003CrespStmt>\n                    \u003Cname xml:id=\"MR\">Maria Randazzo\u003C/name>\n                    \u003Cresp>autopsy and editing\u003C/resp>\n                \u003C/respStmt>\n                \u003CrespStmt>\n                    \u003Cname xml:id=\"VF\" ref=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-6302-3726\">Victoria Fendel\u003C/name>\n                    \u003Cresp>lemmatization and linguistic analysis\u003C/resp>\n                \u003C/respStmt>\n            \u003C/titleStmt>\n            \u003CpublicationStmt>\n                \u003Cauthority>I.Sicily\u003C/authority>\n                \u003Cidno type=\"filename\">ISic000056\u003C/idno>\n                \u003Cidno type=\"TM\">284852\u003C/idno>\n                \u003Cidno type=\"EDR\">111049\u003C/idno>\n                \u003Cidno type=\"EDH\"/>\n                \u003Cidno type=\"EDCS\">22100092\u003C/idno>\n                \u003Cidno type=\"PHI\"/>\n                \u003Cidno type=\"URI\">http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic000056\u003C/idno>\n                \u003Cidno type=\"DOI\" when=\"2020-12-17\">10.5281/zenodo.4333926\u003C/idno>\n                \u003Cavailability>\n                    \u003Clicence target=\"http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/\">Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence.\u003C/licence>\n                \u003C/availability>\n            \u003C/publicationStmt>\n            \u003CsourceDesc>\n                \u003CmsDesc>\n                    \u003CmsIdentifier>\n                        \u003Ccountry>Italy\u003C/country>\n                        \u003Cregion>Sicily\u003C/region>\n                        \u003Csettlement>Palermo\u003C/settlement>\n                        \u003Crepository role=\"museum\" ref=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/museum/064\">Museo Archeologico Regionale Antonino Salinas\u003C/repository>\n                        \u003Cidno type=\"inventory\">3556\u003C/idno>\n                        \u003C!--Adding location for old id numbers if available-->\n                        \u003CaltIdentifier>\n                            \u003Csettlement/>\n                            \u003Crepository/>\n                            \u003Cidno type=\"old\"/>\n                        \u003C/altIdentifier>\n                    \u003C/msIdentifier>\n                    \u003CmsContents>\n                        \u003CtextLang mainLang=\"la\">Latin\u003C/textLang>\n                    \u003C/msContents>\n                    \u003CphysDesc>\n                        \u003CobjectDesc>\n                            \u003CsupportDesc>\n                                \u003Csupport>\n                                    \u003Cp>Quadrangular plaque of grey marble with white veining. Minor damage to the lower right corner only, which does not affect the epigraphic text. The edges are all cut regularly. The lower edge has two small holes (8 mm), probably of modern date for display.\u003C/p>\n                                    \u003Cmaterial ana=\"#material.stone.marble\" ref=\"http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/material/lod/48.html\">marble\u003C/material>\n                                    \u003CobjectType ana=\"#object.plaque\" ref=\"https://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/objtyp/lod/259.html\">plaque\u003C/objectType>\n                                    \u003Cdimensions>\n                                        \u003Cheight unit=\"cm\">23\u003C/height>\n                                        \u003Cwidth unit=\"cm\">25.5\u003C/width>\n                                        \u003Cdepth unit=\"cm\">4\u003C/depth>\n                                    \u003C/dimensions>\n                                \u003C/support>\n                                \u003Ccondition ana=\"#condition.damaged\"/>\n                            \u003C/supportDesc>\n                            \u003ClayoutDesc>\n                                \u003Clayout>\n                                    \u003Cp>The epigraphic field, of three lines of Latin letters, decreasing in size, is approximately centred on the plaque, with an upper margin of 4.5cm, a lower margin of 1.8cm, left margin of 2.5 cm and right margin of 2 cm.\u003C/p>\n                                    \u003Crs ana=\"#execution.chiselled\" ref=\"http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/writing/lod/1\">chiselled\u003C/rs>\n                                    \u003Cdamage ana=\"#text_condition.complete\"/>\n                                \u003C/layout>\n                            \u003C/layoutDesc>\n                        \u003C/objectDesc>\n                        \u003ChandDesc>\n                            \u003ChandNote>\n                                \u003Cp>The letters are v-cut in a tall and narrow module, with triangular serifs. The letters are regularly spaced, with the size / spacing decreasing towards the right and from line 1 to line 3. A has a cross bar descending to the left; M has four full length strokes, all off vertical. Interpuncts in the form of ivy-leaf (somewhat various in form) at the end of each line; plainer interpuncts between words in line 3.\u003C/p>\n                                \u003Clocus from=\"line1\" to=\"line1\">Line 1\u003C/locus>\n                                \u003Cdimensions type=\"letterHeight\">\n                                    \u003Cheight unit=\"mm\" atLeast=\"55\" atMost=\"55\">55\u003C/height>\n                                \u003C/dimensions>\n                                \u003Clocus from=\"line2\" to=\"line2\">Line 2\u003C/locus>\n                                \u003Cdimensions type=\"letterHeight\">\n                                    \u003Cheight unit=\"mm\" atLeast=\"52\" atMost=\"52\">52\u003C/height>\n                                \u003C/dimensions>\n                                \u003Clocus from=\"line3\" to=\"line3\">Line 3\u003C/locus>\n                                \u003Cdimensions type=\"letterHeight\">\n                                    \u003Cheight unit=\"mm\" atLeast=\"30\" atMost=\"30\">30\u003C/height>\n                                \u003C/dimensions>\n                                \u003Clocus from=\"line1\" to=\"line2\"/>\n                                \u003Cdimensions type=\"interlinear\">\n                                    \u003Cheight unit=\"mm\" atLeast=\"25\" atMost=\"25\">25\u003C/height>\n                                \u003C/dimensions>\n                                \u003Clocus from=\"line2\" to=\"line3\"/>\n                                \u003Cdimensions type=\"interlinear\">\n                                    \u003Cheight unit=\"mm\" atLeast=\"15\" atMost=\"15\">15\u003C/height>\n                                \u003C/dimensions>\n                            \u003C/handNote>\n                        \u003C/handDesc>\n                    \u003C/physDesc>\n                    \u003Chistory>\n                        \u003Corigin>\n                            \u003CorigPlace>\u003Cregion>Sicilia\u003C/region>\n                                \u003CplaceName type=\"ancient\" ref=\"http://pleiades.stoa.org/places/462513\" cert=\"low\">Thermae Himeraeae\u003C/placeName>\n                                \u003CplaceName type=\"modern\" ref=\"http://sws.geonames.org/6539140\">Termini Imerese\u003C/placeName>\n                                \u003Cgeo>37.98365, 13.69555\u003C/geo>\n                            \u003C/origPlace>\n                            \u003CorigDate datingMethod=\"#julian\" notBefore-custom=\"0001\" notAfter-custom=\"0100\">1st century CE\u003C/origDate>\n                        \u003C/origin>\n                        \u003Cprovenance type=\"found\" subtype=\"first-seen\" when=\"1867\">First recorded in Termini Imerese in 1867 by Benndorf who saw it at an antique dealer, who subsequently sold it to Palermo museum.\u003C/provenance>\n                        \u003Cprovenance type=\"observed\" subtype=\"autopsied\" resp=\"#MR\">Maria Randazzo 2022-05-23, Museo Archeologico Regionale, Palermo, on display in the courtyard.\u003C/provenance>\n                        \u003Cacquisition/>\n                    \u003C/history>\n                \u003C/msDesc>\n            \u003C/sourceDesc>\n        \u003C/fileDesc>\n        \u003CencodingDesc>\n            \u003Cp>Encoded following the latest EpiDoc guidelines\u003C/p>\n            \u003Cxi:include href=\"../alists/ISicily-taxonomies.xml\">\n                \u003Cxi:fallback>\n                    \u003Cp>Taxonomies for ISicily controlled values\u003C/p>\n                \u003C/xi:fallback>\n            \u003C/xi:include>\n            \u003Cxi:include href=\"../alists/charDecl.xml\">\n                \u003Cxi:fallback>\n                    \u003Cp>ISicily glyphs authority list\u003C/p>\n                \u003C/xi:fallback>\n            \u003C/xi:include>\n        \u003C/encodingDesc>\n        \u003CprofileDesc>\n            \u003CcalendarDesc>\n                \u003Ccalendar xml:id=\"julian\">\n                    \u003Cp>Julian Calendar\u003C/p>\n                \u003C/calendar>\n            \u003C/calendarDesc>\n            \u003ClangUsage>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"en\">English\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"it\">Italian\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"grc\">Ancient Greek\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"la\">Latin\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"he\">Hebrew\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"phn\">Phoenician\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"xpu\">Punic\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"osc\">Oscan\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"xly\">Elymian\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"scx\">Sikel\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"sxc\">Sikan\u003C/language>\n            \u003C/langUsage>\n            \u003CtextClass>\n                \u003Ckeywords scheme=\"http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/typeins.html\">\n                    \u003Cterm ana=\"#function.funerary\" ref=\"http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/typeins/lod/92.html\">funerary\u003C/term>\n                \u003C/keywords>\n            \u003C/textClass>\n        \u003C/profileDesc>\n        \u003CrevisionDesc status=\"draft\">\n            \u003ClistChange>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2016-12-03\" who=\"#JCu\">James Cummings autogenerated EpiDoc output from database\u003C/change>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2018-05-11\" who=\"#TA\">Tuuli Ahlholm cleaned up the autogenerated text and added an apparatus\u003C/change>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2020-10-05\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova normalised Unicode\u003C/change>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2020-10-07\" who=\"#VM\">Valentina Mignosa encoded text division\u003C/change>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2020-10-08\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova updated list of languages\u003C/change>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2020-11-20\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova added EDCS numbers\u003C/change>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2020-11-26\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova restructured bibliography\u003C/change>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2020-12-17\" who=\"#JP\">Updated Zenodo DOI\u003C/change>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2021-01-19\" who=\"#SS\">renumbered files, uris and references\u003C/change>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2022-05-23\" who=\"#MR\">Maria Randazzo edited file from autopsy and added commentary\u003C/change>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2022-06-16\" who=\"#JP\">Jonathan Prag edited and added image\u003C/change>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2025-07-24\" who=\"#VF\">Victoria Fendel's lemmatizations were added\u003C/change>\n            \u003C/listChange>\n        \u003C/revisionDesc>\n    \u003C/teiHeader>\n    \u003Cfacsimile>\n        \u003Csurface type=\"front\">\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"screen\" url=\"ISic000056_tiled.tif\" height=\"3346px\" width=\"3231px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>Photo J. Prag, courtesy  Museo Archeologico Regionale Antonino Salinas\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"print\" url=\"ISic000056.jpg\" height=\"3346px\" width=\"3231px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>Photo J. Prag, courtesy  Museo Archeologico Regionale Antonino Salinas\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n        \u003C/surface>\n    \u003C/facsimile>\n    \u003Ctext>\n        \u003Cbody>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"edition\" subtype=\"primary\" xml:space=\"preserve\" xml:lang=\"la\" resp=\"#MR\">\n                \u003Cab>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"1\"/>\u003CpersName type=\"attested\"> \u003Cname type=\"nomen\">\u003Cw n=\"5\">\u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>Claud\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>ius\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan>\u003C/w>\u003C/name> \u003Cg ref=\"#ivy-leaf\" n=\"10\">❦\u003C/g>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"2\"/>\u003Cname type=\"cognomen\">\u003Cw n=\"15\">Maximus\u003C/w>\u003C/name>\u003C/persName> \u003Cg ref=\"#ivy-leaf\" n=\"20\">❦\u003C/g>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"3\"/>\u003Cw n=\"25\">\u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>vix\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>it\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan>\u003C/w> \u003Cg ref=\"#ivy-leaf\" n=\"30\">❦\u003C/g> \u003Cw n=\"35\">\u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>an\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>nis\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan>\u003C/w> \u003Cunclear>\u003Cg ref=\"#ivy-leaf\" n=\"40\">❦\u003C/g>\u003C/unclear> \u003Cnum value=\"17\">\u003Cw n=\"45\">XVII\u003C/w>\u003C/num> \u003Cg ref=\"#ivy-leaf\" n=\"50\">❦\u003C/g>\n                \u003C/ab>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"edition\" subtype=\"simple-lemmatized\" resp=\"#VF\">\n                \u003Cab>\n                    \u003Cw n=\"5\" lemma=\"Claudius\">Claudius\u003C/w>\n                    \u003Cw n=\"15\" lemma=\"Maximus\">Maximus\u003C/w>\n                    \u003Cw n=\"25\" lemma=\"vivo\">vixit\u003C/w>\n                    \u003Cw n=\"35\" lemma=\"annus\">annis\u003C/w>\n                    \u003Cw n=\"45\" lemma=\"XVII\">XVII\u003C/w>\n                \u003C/ab>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"apparatus\">\n                \u003ClistApp>\n                    \u003Capp>\n                        \u003Cnote>Text from autopsy\u003C/note>\n                    \u003C/app>\n                \u003C/listApp>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"translation\" xml:lang=\"it\" resp=\"#MR\">\n                \u003Cp>Claudio Massimo, visse per anni diciassette.\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"translation\" xml:lang=\"en\" resp=\"#JP\">\n                \u003Cp>Claudius Maximus lived for 17 years.\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"commentary\" resp=\"#MR\" xml:lang=\"it\">\n                \u003Cp>La lettura del testo è sostanzialmente identica alle edizioni precedenti (Mommsen- C.I.L. X - Bivona 1970). Il commento si discosta dall'edizione di Mommsen (l'unica a riportare i segni d'interpunzione) per l'interpretazione dei segni divisori, nelle linee 2 e 3, come piccole foglie d'edera stilizzate: questa lettura si deve al particolare del tratto allungato verso destra, più simile al gambo d'edera della prima linea (per quanto la grandezza differisce molto) che ad un semplice segno a sezione triangolare; inoltre, tra l'abbreviazione \"an\" di \"annis\" e il numerale \"XVII\", si scorge un segno obliquo molto simile al carattere prima descritto e quindi considerato come un segno divisorio a foglia d'edera incerto.\u003C/p>\n                \u003Cp>L'epigrafe funeraria è molto semplice, con formulario estremamente sintetico: viene riportato il nome del defunto (composto esclusivamente di nomen e cognomen) e la durata della vita. Sulla base di questa particolarità, Bivona data l'iscrizione ad un periodo antecedente a Marco Aurelio in quanto fu quest'ultimo a regolarizzare le norme sui tria nomina. La studiosa ricorda infatti che il praenomen, prima di quest'epoca, veniva assunto al compimento del diciassettesimo anno di vita con l'assunzione della toga virile; cerimonia che evidentemente in questo caso non era ancora avvenuta. Secondo il Mommsen, il reperto fu segnalato in un mercato antiquario a Termini Imerese nel 1867 da Benndorf. In un'età imprecisata, ma verosimilmente non in antico, furono ricavati due piccoli fori sullo spessore inferiore, probabilmente per l'esposizione della lastra.\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"bibliography\">\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"edition\">\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"corpus\" n=\"CIL\">\n                        \u003Cauthor>Mommsen\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1883\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>\n                            \u003Cref target=\"http://arachne.uni-koeln.de/item/buchseite/650798\">7391\u003C/ref>\n                        \u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/GQN8UZSI\"/>\n                        \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589\u003C/ref>\n                    \u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"corpus\" n=\"ILMusPalermo\">\n                         \u003Cauthor>Bivona\u003C/author>\n                         \u003Cdate>1970\u003C/date> \n                        \u003CcitedRange>56\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/FZWWPUD6\"/>\n                        \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002142\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002142\u003C/ref>\n                    \u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"corpus\" n=\"ILMusTermini\">\n                         \u003Cauthor>Bivona\u003C/author>\n                         \u003Cdate>1994\u003C/date> \n                        \u003CcitedRange>72\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/JCV85C79\"/>\n                        \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002137\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002137\u003C/ref>\n                    \u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl/>\n                \u003C/listBibl>\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"discussion\">\n                    \u003Cbibl/>\n                \u003C/listBibl>\n            \u003C/div>\n        \u003C/body>\n    \u003C/text>\n\u003C/TEI>"],"uses":{"params":["slug"]}}]}
